social_posts.post_text: H-Town royalty has arrived 😎

HAPPY BIRTHDAY ASHHHHHH!!! We have been through so many moments of our lives together- from navigating industry parties, to always being first in line for photo booths, to only seeing each other on Skype for awhile 😅, our Ryan Gosling phase (that we still haven’t grown out of yet), to pre planning your wedding on Pinterest even though you weren’t engaged yet, to then actually GETTING married and being your Maid of Honor and soooo many other amazing, funny, crazy memories in between. You are a true gem of a person and I am so lucky you are my best friend! I love you!!! 30, here she comes💜🥳🎉

Let’s get ready to rumble!
